text: Timothy Lahner (born 16 April 1966) is a South African rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:South African male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Africa Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
